steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Mobile app" with submenu "Mobile Editor"
Then I should see Mobile screen display
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I add new screen with name JIT040ImagePickerPreviewCode
Then I should see the screen with name JIT040ImagePickerPreviewCode display in list Pages
When I select screen with name JIT040ImagePickerPreviewCode
When I select tab list with name "Layers"
When I open Search popup on item value "JIT040ImagePickerPreviewCode" with index "1"
When I add item "Image Picker" in Search popup with sub menu "Form" to preview mobile editor
When I open preview code with component mode
Then I should see the code content "M40a_MAIN_IMAGEPICKER_INIT"
When I close preview code panel
When I toggle on item value "JIT040ImagePickerPreviewCode" with index "1"
When I select item value "ImagePicker" with index "1"
When I toggle off Layout tree header
When I select field label "Launcher Type" of header "ImagePicker" with radio "default"
When I update field label "Width" of header "Basic" with radio "%" and value "100"
